# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [1.0.0] - 2015-04-22
### Added
- Initial Release

## [1.0.1] - 2015-04-23
### Fixed
- Bug fix for PHP 5.3 compatibility

## [1.0.2] - 2015-04-30
### Added
- Compatibility with Concrete5.7.4

## [1.0.4] - 2015-05-01
### Added
- Added 'Author' and 'Approved By' standard page attribute filters.

### Updated
- 'Preview' will no longer show anything if the user is not logged in.

### Fixed
- Bug fix for compatibility issues with c5.7.4

## [1.1.0] - 2015-05-26
### Added
- Functionality to be able to extend Page List+ with custom attribute filters.

### Fixed
- Installation errors

## [1.1.1] - 2015-05-28
### Fixed
- Installation errors

## [1.1.2] - 2015-06-01
### Added
- Customizing the pagination

### Fixed
- Block settings not being saved: page location and hide current page
- Required core javascript file

## [1.1.3] - 2015-06-15
### Fixed
- Bugs in the 'Topics' filter

## [1.1.4] - 2015-06-25
### Added
- Exact and partial matches for filtering by a Topic attribute

### Fixed
- Bugs in the Page Selection
- Bugs in the Filtering
- Showing/not showing a thumbnail

## [1.1.5] - 2015-07-12
### Fixed
- Issue when relating results to keywords/content in areas
- Issue when editing a Page List+ block in a stack
- Loading throbber image

## [1.2.0] - 2015-09-14
### Added
- Thumbnail Grid Block Template
- Find pages 'in the current branch' and 'at the Parent Level' in the Page Selection tab

### Fixed
- Compatibility with concrete5 v5.7.5.2
- Search Target URL in search
- RSS Feed functionality
- JavaScript issue when visitor is not logged in
- Filter by Author

## [1.2.1] - 2015-09-15
### Fixed
- Bug in version number

## [1.2.2] - 2015-09-18
### Added
- Validation for RSS feed title and URL slug

### Fixed
- Bug in 'Display Pages that are Located...'
- Bug using 'after' in date filters

## [1.2.3] - 2015-09-20
### Fixed
- Bug with RSS when saving

## [1.2.4] - 2015-10-02
### Added
- Multi-Date compatibility (ProEvents)

### Fixed
- Bug with JavaScript inclusion

## [1.2.5] - 2015-10-05
### Fixed
- Bug in pagination

## [1.2.6] - 2015-10-07
### Fixed
- Bug in the 'Show All' link

## [1.2.7] - 2015-10-28
### Added
- New Date/Time filters: is last year, is this year, is next year, in last 12 months, in next 12 months

## [1.2.8] - 2015-11-02
### Fixed
- Bug in search when not showing all results on page load
- Adding CSS to display pagination correctly

## [1.2.9] - 2015-11-20
### Fixed
- Bug that results in an empty page list

## [1.2.10] - 2016-01-07
### Fixed
- Bug fix for array bug in attribute filters

### Added
- Page Selector compatibility (for use with the Page Selector attribute package)
- Sortable attribute filters in the search tab. Drag and drop the checked boxes.

## [1.2.11] - 2016-01-08
### Fixed
- Installation error

## [1.2.12] - 2016-01-19
### Fixed
- Custom sorting in concrete5.7.5.4

## [1.3.0] - 2016-01-28
### Updated
- PHP7 compatibility

### Fixed
- Filters that were not showing on front-facing forms

## [1.3.1] - 2016-02-03
### Added
- Fulltext search capabilities
- Automatically disables 'Relevance' sorting when querystring is not used

## [1.3.2] - 2016-02-10
### Fixed
- Page Type filter preview and JS error
- Page Template filter preview and JS error
- Page Theme filter preview and JS error
- Skip 'x' number of pages

## [1.3.3] - 2016-04-18
### Fixed
- Filtering date attributes
- Displaying aliased pages

## [1.3.4] - 2016-04-20
### Fixed
- Filtering date attributes in search
